  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0004",
    "kind": "section_text_panel",
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "primary_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_2",
    "source": "header_anchor",
    "member_count": 6,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_2",
        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "早寒有怀",
        "bbox": [
          0.2476305706795725,
          0.1145788798631894,
          0.3194192377495463,
          0.12825994014536127
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_19",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "抑扬是古代诗歌传情达意产曲折美的一种常见 手法。抑是否定、贬损，扬是肯定、称颂。抑扬是指在 诗歌作品中对人物或事物、事件等采取的欲扬先抑或 欲抑先扬的手法，而使人物的性格或精神、事物的特 征、事件的性质等在前后对比中发变化，使情感内涵 形成反差，使叙述、抒情构成波折，从而吸引读者，增强 作品的感染。",
        "bbox": [
          0.5057471264367817,
          0.11799914493373237,
          0.9219600725952813,
          0.23200798061849792
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "孟浩然",
        "bbox": [
          0.2573099415204678,
          0.13168020521590423,
          0.30973986690865096,
          0.14479122131965227
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_4",
        "observed_type": "list",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "木落雁南度，北风江上寒。 我家襄水曲，遥隔楚云端。 乡泪客中尽，归帆天际看。 迷津欲有问，平海夕漫漫。",
        "bbox": [
          0.18471466021375277,
          0.1470713980333476,
          0.39120790481952006,
          0.21148639019524013
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "【注】 ①迷津：迷路。",
        "bbox": [
          0.1088929219600726,
          0.21319652273051162,
          0.2710223835450696,
          0.22801767136953113
        ],
        "order": 9
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_6",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "这诗以“平海漫漫”作结，有何妙处？请简要 分析。",
        "bbox": [
          0.07582173825368017,
          0.22972780390480263,
          0.489614841701956,
          0.2610802337181132
        ],
        "order": 10
      }
    ]
  },
