  },
  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0007",
    "kind": "section_text_panel",
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188",
    "primary_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_22",
    "source": "header_anchor",
    "member_count": 7,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_22",
        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "咏山泉",
        "bbox": [
          0.686428715466828,
          0.3004132820293573,
          0.741278483565235,
          0.31409434231152916
        ],
        "order": 15
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "照应是指诗歌篇章间的伏笔照应，又叫呼应，是古 典诗歌常见的种结构形式。诗不论律诗还是绝 句，都应有头有尾，前后内容就要有内在联系，前面交 待过的话，后面得有照应；后边要照应的话，前边得先 有个交待，形成个有机的整体，这样，诗歌前后才能 贯串，情节连贯、脉络清晰、结构紧凑，使读者容易掌握 全诗的脉络。",
        "bbox": [
          0.07582173825368017,
          0.31580447484680063,
          0.49122807017543857,
          0.4298133105315662
        ],
        "order": 16
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_23",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "储光羲",
        "bbox": [
          0.686428715466828,
          0.3169445632036483,
          0.7404718693284936,
          0.33062562348582014
        ],
        "order": 17
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_24",
        "observed_type": "list",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "山中有流水，借问不知名。 映地为天色，飞空作雨声。 转来深涧满，分出小池平。 恬淡无人见，年年长自清。",
        "bbox": [
          0.6146400483968542,
          0.3329058001995155,
          0.81387376487195,
          0.39618070400456035
        ],
        "order": 18
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_25",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "结合全诗，简要分析“映地为天，飞空作声”的 妙处。",
        "bbox": [
          0.5073603549102642,
          0.39846088071825564,
          0.92115345835854,
          0.42924326635314236
        ],
        "order": 19
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_10",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "尾照应，即开头与结尾的照应，这样照应使诗歌 在结构上有浑然一体之感，能更加突出主题，起到良好 的表达效果。在些诗歌中，诗往往采今昔、他 我、物我照应的式，来抒发自己或他人情感。",
        "bbox": [
          0.0750151240169389,
          0.43152344306683765,
          0.4920346844121799,
          0.49650847940715404
        ],
        "order": 20
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_26",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "答：",
        "bbox": [
          0.5226860254083484,
          0.43209348724526153,
          0.9219600725952813,
          0.46401596123699584
        ],
        "order": 21
      }
    ]
  },
