        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "三、四两句欲扬先抑，写得意味深长。请作简要 赏析。",
        "bbox": [
          0.5226860254083484,
          0.6127974918056149,
          0.9203468441217988,
          0.6441499216189255
        ],
        "order": 33
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_188_16",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "律诗的尾讲究回呼照应，试分析这诗的联 和尾联是如何照应的。",
        "bbox": [
          0.07582173825368017,
